    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3019">Robbertus</persName>,
                        divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, ad
                        salutem ac remedium animarum quondam <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            >gloriosorum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #grandparentOf"
                            ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName> scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf"
                            >avi</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs>, et <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #siblingOf"
                            ref="#people/3010">secundi Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratris</rs>, et anime nostre salutem, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">interventu</rs> quoque <persName key="#Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/3040">Hugonis de la Bulita</persName> et aliorum baronum
                        fidelium nostrorum, per hoc principale scriptum, imperpetuum, damus, et
                        concedimus ac confirmamus <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Immunity #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3001">Sancti
                            Blasii </orgName>de <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000"
                            >Aversa</placeName>, unoquoque die anni, <rs
                            key="#Forests #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >de lignis nostre silve</rs>salmas quattuor, scilicet in estate, in
                            <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4502"><geogName
                                key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/3019">Porcile</geogName></placeName> et tempore vernis
                        in <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/4503"><geogName
                                key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/3020">Esclito</geogName></placeName>, ita ut
                        potestatem habeant homines ipsius monasterii incidendi in ipsis silvis
                        nostris, ut prediximus, unoquoque die, salmas quattuor, et deferendi ad opus
                        ipsius monasterii et ancillarum Dei, qui ibi omnipotenti Deo serviunt, <rs
                            key="#Immunity">absque omni contrarietate nostra et molestia, et omnium
                            principum successorum nostrorum, et omnium servientium, et ordinatorum
                            nostre curie</rs>. Quod si quis huius nostre dationis et concessionis
                        pagine contemptor aut violator extiterit, <rs key="#Penalty">quattuor libras
                            auri </rs>componat, medietatem ipsi monasterio, et medietatem nostre
                        curie. Et soluta pena librarum, hec nostra datio et concessio firma
                        permaneat ìmperpetuum; et ut hoc scriptum firmius credatur et diligentius ab
                        omnibus observetur, ex nostro sigillo iussimus illud insigniri. Ex iussione
                        prephate potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3012">Quiriacus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> preceptum istud, in anno dominice incarnationis
                        millesimo centesimo decimo sexto, et decimo anno principatus ipsius domni
                        Robberti principis. Datum apud <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000"
                            >Aversanam</placeName> urbem, in <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Domus" ref="#people/3085">Richardi Musce</persName>, mense
                        iulio, per indictionem nonam, ante <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Raginaldus de Matalone">Raynaldum de
                        Matalone</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Richardus fil. Ioffridi">Richardum filii
                            Ioffridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3035"
                            >Odoaldum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">camerarium</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Bernardus fil. Widonis">Bernardum filium
                            Guidi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Viscount"
                            ref="#people/3086">Iohannem</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitem</rs>.</ab>
